<p><span class="anchor" id="p56"></span>هزقا نشط وَفِي الضحك أَكثر مِنْهُ<a href="#p56" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p57"></span><span class="c2">(أهزق)</span> فِي الضحك هزق فِيهِ<a href="#p57" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p58"></span><span class="c2">(المهزاق)</span> من النَّاس الضَّحَّاك الْخَفِيف<a href="#p58" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>